COMMENT ON COLUMN "public"."flag_targets"."meets_sbti_minimum" IS 'Whether the target meets SBTi FLAG v1.2 minimum stringency: near-term (by 2030) >= 30% absolute; long-term (by 2050) >= 72% absolute.';



